column3: “This Indica by Inhalence contained 12% THC. Mild fruity sweetness was the scent & flavor. Packed, hunter green buds with small fine trichomes & short, thin, pale pistils. The high was  smooth, relaxing, mellow, calm, & chill. Nice body relaxation with no head games. Protect The Harvest.....”
“It's one of the best and most potent buds I've gotten in a while”
